  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to gpgmepp</title>

    <para>
      The <application>gpgmepp</application> package provides a 
      C++ wrapper to <xref linkend="gpgme"/>.
    </para>

    &lfs123_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&gpgmepp-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (FTP): <ulink url="&gpgmepp-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download MD5 sum: &gpgmepp-md5sum;
        </para>
